message: Unfortunately I do believe that having 'Hush Puppy' as a redirect link to the type of food of which is spelt differently is bizarre... This act does not have an article and is arguably "notable".
Page for artist 'Hush Puppy' was non-existent and Wiki title was the correction of a misspelling.
Recycled redirect link to the appropriate artist.
